column5: I was wondering if the parks tore has any worms. I'm doubting they have leeches, any nearby places to buy some? And any tips on the walleye would be appreciated.

there is a place just about 4 mins down the road called round lake ceter,its like the general store and gas station they have worms,and im sure minnows as well...lots of spots have worms all around there you will be fine !!! cheers
